    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Small decorative or functional objects, typically attached to a chain or strap hanging from a pocket or within a purse, such as fobs for a watch or key. When decorative, they often serve as jewelry.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
